    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The CFD model predicts RH < 1.0 across all five operating points, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The validation team concluded that the numerical simulation provides sufficient evidence of hemolysis performance, noting that the Giersiepen model has been extensively calibrated against experimental data and that the simulation results are considered functionally equivalent to direct experimental measurement. The six non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scoping. The credibility assessment is accepted and the model is judged fit for the stated COU.",
